Well they never - every normal way. We daresn't answer me father back unless - it was in some argument as you knew me father was in the wrong, or me mother was in the wrong. But that was very very rare. No one had - cause to complain of anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 
But your parents would expect you to be obedient, they expected you to come in at certain times and expected you to accept their rules and regulations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1265594 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your sisters and brothers in cer
tain ways? You said everybody was supposed to help everybody else didn't you?
