were - go for open your mouth - you'd only got to put his finger up like that and you daren't open - you daresn't - you'd got to - to choke yourself with that words which you were going to say back again until they'd finished, and then you could - broach 
your subject on whatever you - you were going to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 If you did something that your parents disapproved of what would happen?
