father'd hit me - perhaps me mother'd - if you said anything - or did anything to one or the other girls or - just a clout, side of the ear}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14253099\charrsid2163176 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 hole - just clip your ears for you you see.
