\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1265594 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14253099\charrsid2163176 Me }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 
dad'd give us that. We used to have the - used to have the belt, as he used to keep - keep a - a strap hanging beside of him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 Can you remember any occasion on which you did get a good hiding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1265594 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 No. No. I can't remember having anything - any
 good hiding, I can't remember any - anyone of the girls having one either. Only - it was Margaret, the - my eldest sister - she did something outside and me father could see what was happening and he didn't shout to her or - he just went out to her, she 
said, now what have you done that for? Now don't - in. You daresn't say - no or - I'm not coming in, you'll hit me, you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14253099\charrsid2163176 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 
d got to go in. And if he didn't feel as he wanted to use the - the strap on you, all as he did, undress, upstairs. You couldn't say, no, I'm not going upstairs. You'd got to go. And you'd stop there until he told you to come down.
\par 
