 playmates - parent's'd - well you'd better take - you're going to this party you'd better take a little bit of a present, such as a - stockings or - or such - clothing or something - as you were - as they'd seen perhaps as - you'd been lacking of but it 
was - I can't think of anything as we were ever lacking, in clothing or anything like that.
