 - me father's eldest son, William, he used to come from Woolstanton perhaps with his wife and two children. And - the other sister - she used to - bring a friend in. But only for teatime but not for dinner. There was only our own family at dinner. Christ
mas dinner. Teatime there used to be - well - used to be what you might say the front place. The parlour had to be used. Such occasions. And there was the three rooms all going all together.
