\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 Did you go to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1265594 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 That every Friday. Tuesday - every Tuesday and Friday. We used to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 You'd go to that as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1265594 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 Oh yes, yes. We were allowed to go anywhere like that. Because they knowed they didn't keep 'em - keep the children out too late.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 Did you belong to the chapel choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1265594 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 Did the chapel run any kind of temperance club, the Band of Hope is a temperance thing isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1265594 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 Well they - they did run some kind of a club but - I never had any activities or - whether me parents - I
 think me father did in any case, 'cos - one of his big friends, of one as I take my second name from - Mr Jess Shirley - what they call Jess Shirley's Bone Works, he used to run that, well - I took his son's name. I was christened Wilfred after}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6906572\charrsid2163176  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 Were there any other clubs belonging to the chapel that you belonged to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1265594 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 Well - we used to run a kind of a clothing club a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6906572\charrsid2163176 
s you could pay coppers in week}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 ly. And - it'd help your parents to buy i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6906572\charrsid2163176 n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 different clothing for you. 'Cos it was more or less done for the poorer class to help them to get decent clothes for - for the charity - the anniversaries.
