\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 So what would they do, they'd set these cocks on to fight one another?
