Bronchial pneumonia. Influenza. And deafness in the second degree. That was - the - well - the second and half degree, it was only half a degree leaving me between complete deafness.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2966169\charrsid2163176 So now we're up to 1919?
