m finished, you get off. So - I went in the orderly room and give me this letter, they opened it and - we're not going to be sto}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16064038\charrsid2163176 p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
